    Reporting model, comprising JGiven's report model, additional fields and Mustache template methods. The reporting model contains all information that can be used to generate a report. Template methods can be used for more advanced manipulation that cannot be handled by out-of-the-box Mustache engine functions.

    Reporters may use it as is, or extend it with even more fields and template methods per need.

    Reports are generated by invoking the Mustache engine with a specific template and a report model.
